Readme for build.xml:

In the build.xml, the default target for the project is "run". So if you
want to run tests, you should change default="runtests" or just launch the
target of "runtests" by command line.

The directory bin, dist, report are created by running build.xml:
The bin directory includes all .class files.
The dist directory include the executable .jar file.
The report directory includes all .xml files which are the test reports for all test cases.
